LogData.text: Saw Noémie pass by earlier, hiding an injury on her arm. I don’t even think it’s the first time she’s taking care of her wounds herself. As the doctor here I’m inclined to believe that it would be better if I did that, but no she’s too stubborn to even try to be professional. She told me to fuck off. Forgive me for caring, I’ll remember to not do that again.
